⚠️ BEFORE YOU START (2 Minutes)
What you need: Microsoft 365 Copilot (paid license). Free Copilot Chat can't access your work emails, files, or meetings — which is where all the magic happens. Ask your IT team if you're unsure.
One setting to change now: In any Copilot chat, look for the model selector at the bottom. You have three modes:
	Quick — fast, simple answers.
	Auto — Copilot picks for you (default).
	Think Deeper — slower but smarter; use this for analysis, strategy, and anything that matters.
Rule of thumb: If you'd spend more than 5 minutes thinking about it yourself, use Think Deeper.
